{"tid":519892,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"2017世界各地如何迎接新年","createTime":"2018-01-04T23:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T23:45:34.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"03055930f415e57f3768e5b594b2e9052e859c15","tid":519892,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T23:45:34.000Z","msg":"隨著地球轉動，世界各地陸續迎來新的一年；從東半球到西半球，或燦爛或寧靜的畫面為2018年揭開序幕。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/976/cpsprodpb/121F8/production/_99423247_gettyimages-900092390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef-1.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F976%2Fcpsprodpb%2F121F8%2Fproduction%2F_99423247_gettyimages-900092390.jpg&h=73b18292&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印尼日惹，煙火在午夜燃亮城市天際線<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/976/cpsprodpb/7A00/production/_99423213_hi043790239.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef-1.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F976%2Fcpsprodpb%2F7A00%2Fproduction%2F_99423213_hi043790239.jpg&h=1de60b05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港維多利亞港除夕與新年交接的夜空<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/936/cpsprodpb/C820/production/_99423215_hi043789273.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef-1.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F936%2Fcpsprodpb%2FC820%2Fproduction%2F_99423215_hi043789273.jpg&h=145b83f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n煙花瞬間遮蓋了馬來西亞吉隆坡的雙峰塔<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/936/cpsprodpb/85B8/production/_99423243_hi043790854.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F936%2Fcpsprodpb%2F85B8%2Fproduction%2F_99423243_hi043790854.jpg&h=9075ecfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n回到印尼，信徒聚集在婆羅浮屠放孔明燈<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/936/cpsprodpb/81D0/production/_99423233_hi043788319.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F936%2Fcpsprodpb%2F81D0%2Fproduction%2F_99423233_hi043788319.jpg&h=7ccc2fe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國首爾，123層的樂天世界塔有煙火相伴<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/936/cpsprodpb/3798/production/_99423241_hi043790916.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F936%2Fcpsprodpb%2F3798%2Fproduction%2F_99423241_hi043790916.jpg&h=98fc66f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在埃及開羅，市集中的聖誕老人迎接新年<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/936/cpsprodpb/16C30/production/_99423239_hi043790956.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef-1.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F936%2Fcpsprodpb%2F16C30%2Fproduction%2F_99423239_hi043790956.jpg&h=22fc2b37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雅加達，七彩煙花為商業區鋪上華美裝飾<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/936/cpsprodpb/11640/production/_99423217_hi043788686.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef-1.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F936%2Fcpsprodpb%2F11640%2Fproduction%2F_99423217_hi043788686.jpg&h=99f50aad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n濱海灣一直是新加坡迎接新年的中心地帶<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/936/cpsprodpb/11E10/production/_99423237_hi043791253.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef-1.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F936%2Fcpsprodpb%2F11E10%2Fproduction%2F_99423237_hi043791253.jpg&h=4c49dceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在紐約時報廣場，人們在寒冬中也早早來到現場凖備迎接新年<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/936/cpsprodpb/2FC8/production/_99423221_hi043788407.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef-1.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F936%2Fcpsprodpb%2F2FC8%2Fproduction%2F_99423221_hi043788407.jpg&h=2ea0535f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n悉尼港的煙火，每年都是世界最早傳送到電視屏幕上的跨年場面<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/936/cpsprodpb/16460/production/_99423219_hi043788538.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F936%2Fcpsprodpb%2F16460%2Fproduction%2F_99423219_hi043788538.jpg&h=ba3b3b32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳大利亞東南部的墨爾本，同樣也煙花慶祝新年<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/936/cpsprodpb/D3D8/production/_99423245_hi043790867.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F936%2Fcpsprodpb%2FD3D8%2Fproduction%2F_99423245_hi043790867.jpg&h=b84ae407&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在凱拉尼亞皇家大佛寺（Kelaniya Temple），信眾在新年到來之際祈禱<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/936/cpsprodpb/CFF0/production/_99423235_hi043791284.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef-1.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F936%2Fcpsprodpb%2FCFF0%2Fproduction%2F_99423235_hi043791284.jpg&h=68ca095f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在土耳其伊斯坦布爾，人們聚集在街頭，等候除夕午夜的到來<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/936/cpsprodpb/10D44/production/_99423986_hi043792452.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef-1.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F936%2Fcpsprodpb%2F10D44%2Fproduction%2F_99423986_hi043792452.jpg&h=9c64ecaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在巴黎香榭麗舍大街，大量民眾聚集迎接2018年<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/936/cpsprodpb/15B64/production/_99423988_hi043792408.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef-1.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F936%2Fcpsprodpb%2F15B64%2Fproduction%2F_99423988_hi043792408.jpg&h=0c581866&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在倫敦，大本鐘雖然在修繕當中，但仍然在新年到來之際響起了鐘聲<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/936/cpsprodpb/4DDC/production/_99423991_hi043793576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F936%2Fcpsprodpb%2F4DDC%2Fproduction%2F_99423991_hi043793576.jpg&h=1651764c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在巴西里約熱內盧的科帕卡巴納海灘，人們在夏夜中觀賞新年煙火<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-42531863\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-42531863&d=N40w6QMbBSPJnUFZIxvBrdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=fe55de62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-42531863&h=47555547\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-42531863</a>"}]}